cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM 

This paper deals with image classification using CNNs and proposes a transfer learning approach to improve the robustness of the classification to image distortion. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also discusses the optimization of the CNN filters, which is related to machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of Borda count election method for ranking the filters is related to neural networks (cs.NE). Finally, the evaluation of the proposed approach on datasets is related to multimedia (cs.MM).
